snippet.title: Zeal — Pre-Alpha Arena Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Note this game is on very early stage of development and it's full of placeholders. 
The first playtesting will start in approx 2-3 weeks with 5 classes and 2 gamemodes.
Join our Discord to learn more: https://discord.gg/WH8xuh3


Learn more about the game: https://zealrpg.com/about
Join our community in Discord: https://discord.gg/WH8xuh3
Get Elemental Halo for your future characters: https://zealrpg.com/halo


Zeal is a 3rd person session-based online action RPG where you can customize your character’s build and appearance to fight in various PvP, PvE and mixed modes in instanced combat.

This time with no grinding and no pay to win features.
